msgid "[learningemail 1] It''s a **great way to connect** and be found on the network. Add a description, phone number, and a website to your \"Profile\" page to make it easier for customers, suppliers, and prospects to find you.{0}All companies on Tradeshift have a \"Profile\" page that is visible to other Tradeshift users. And, if you want to be found through Google, Yahoo!, Bing, and other search engines, simply enable your public profile on the \"Public Profile\" settings page. Doing this helps you **grow your business and build your brand**. Customers that are not on Tradeshift will be able to visit your profile and send you Invoices."
msgstr "这是一个很好地建立企业间联系的方式。您可以在“公司信息”上添加一段描述，电话号码以及网站信息，就可以方便地让客户、供应商以及潜在合作伙伴找到您。{0}所有在Tradeshift上注册的公司都有一个对其他用户可见的“公司信息”。如果您希望信息能被Google，Yahoo!，Bing等搜索引擎收录，只需要在“公司信息”的设置页面选择启用“公开资料”，便能帮助您**扩展业务以及提升品牌形象**。即使对方没有使用Tradeshift，也同样能够访问到您的页面并向您发送发票。"

msgid "[learningemail 2] Tradeshift is **designed to save you time managing Invoices** by taking advantage of the latest technology and network functionality.{0}To send an Invoice, click the green **“Create Invoice” button**. Add a recipient (or create a new contact directly from here), and complete the details of your Invoice. The total will be automatically calculated for you.{0}Tradeshift **remembers Invoice data**. Just start typing, and the system will make auto-fill suggestions from previous transactions. You can overwrite information at any time.{0}Search for Invoices sent or received at any time **from the \"Documents\" tab**.{0}*Pro tip: To save more time, use previous Invoices as a draft when you create a similar Invoice (click on an Invoice from your Documents page, then click on \"use as draft\" at the top of the Invoice).*"
msgstr "Tradeshift基于最新的技术以及网络功能，**旨在帮助您更有效地管理发票**。{0}要发送发票，请点击绿色的**“创建发票”**的按钮。添加一个收件人（或直接在此添加新联系人），并完整填写您的发票。总金额会为您自动计算。{0}Tradeshift会**记住发票信息**，在您输入的时候系统会根据之前交易的内容生成自动提示列表以供您选择。当然，您也可以在任何时候重写这些信息。{0}可以随时在“文档”标签中查找发送或者收到的文档。{0}*进阶提示：为了节省时间，您在创建类似的发票时也可以选择之前的发票作为草稿（在您的文档页面打开一个发票，点击其顶部的“用作草稿”）。*"

msgid "[learningemail 2] All Invoices you send or receive in Tradeshift have a status that can be updated by both you and your customer (or supplier if you are the recipient). This way, you''ll **always know the status of your Invoices**, without the need to call or email your contact.{0}Your customer can **accept or reject** your Invoice or **mark it as paid**, in a single click. You can both update the status, displayed in your activity stream - in real time.{0}You can **post comments**, answer questions, or settle disputes, which are private and kept in one place to save you time."
msgstr "您所有通过Tradeshift发送接受的发票都有状态信息，由您或者您的客户/供应商来更新。这样您不需要打电话或者发邮件给您的联系人，就可以**了解发票的状态**。{0}您的客户只需一次点击，就能选择**接受或拒绝**您的发票，或将其标记为已支付。状态更新将会实时反应在最新动态中。{0}您还可以在系统中**添加回复**，回答问题，解决异议。Tradeshift在帮助您省时的同时，对所有信息保密。"

msgid "[learningemail 2] Since **not all** your customers are on the Tradeshift network (not yet!), we made it extremely easy to Invoice them. And they **don''t even have to join Tradeshift**. You''ll still be able to post comments and get Invoice status updates.{0}Simply go to the Invoice \"Create\" page or the \"Network\" tab, search for your customer, and if they are not found on Tradeshift, you can easily fill in their contact information manually. Invoices sent to your new contact will be **received via email as a PDF**. This email will contain a unique link to a page on Tradeshift, where your customer can instantly approve your Invoice."
msgstr "也许您需要向Tradeshift网络之外的客户发送发票，这个很简单。他们**甚至都不需要加入Tradeshift**。而您仍然可以一样发送评论，并得到发票状态的更新消息。你只需要进入发票“创建”页面或者“网络”标签，查找您的客户，如果在Tradeshift上找不到，您可以手动的出入他们的联系信息。发送给他们的发票将会**以PDF格式发往他们的电子邮箱**。电子邮件中包含了一个指向Tradeshift页面的链接，在这个页面上您的客户可以批准通过您的发票。"

msgid "[learningemail 3] Activating an App is easy. Just click \"Apps\" on the top bar and **browse around for features and functions** that best suit your business.{0}Tradeshift Apps work a bit differently than smartphone apps. Once you activate an App inside Tradeshift, **the functionality integrates seamlessly where it makes the most sense**. An App may add functionality to the \"Create Invoice\" page or appear on your Home page (read the individual App description for more information). You can always **access all activated Apps** through the top bar of your profile.{0}Most of the Apps are free, but some Premium Apps are subject to a fee."
msgstr "启用应用软件很简单，点击**“应用软件”标签**之后，即可浏览提供不同功能的应用软件并从中选择最符合您需求的。{0}当您在Tradeshift启用了一个应用软件之后，它将会**无缝地集成到现有系统中**。应用软件可以是为“创建发票”提供额外的功能，也可以显示在您的主页上（请阅读应用软件的描述以了解更多）。您可以在资料页面的顶部选择**访问所有已启用的应用软件**。{0}大多数应用软件都是免费，但也有些需要收取一定费用。"

msgid "[learningemail 4] Reissuing an invoice or discussing a dispute is time consuming. Tradeshift helps you avoid a lot of the typical mistakes by **validating required fields**. Imagine never having to ask \"Have you received my Invoice?\" again.{0}Tradeshift delivers other smart features like remembering Invoice data and payment options and the ability to use previous Invoices as a draft. This way, you''re able to **move quickly and avoid mistakes** at the same time.{0}Also, make sure you **double-check the content** of each Invoice before you hit \"Send\". This usually takes less time than reissuing an Invoice or sending a Credit Note to fix a mistake. Remember, in order to make your Invoices compliant with tax laws, online Invoices sent from Tradeshift can not be changed once sent (just like paper Invoices)."
msgstr "补发发票或讨论争议非常耗费时间。Tradeshift通过**验证必须填写的字段**帮助你避免很多常见的错误。有了Tradeshift，您再也不需要问“您是否收到了我的发票？”。{0}Tradeshift还提供很多智能功能，例如记住发票数据，支付选项并允许使用之前的发票作为模板。这样，您就能**快速完成工作，同时避免错误**。{0}并且, Tradeshift要求每次发送发票前**再次检查发票内容**。这样通常比补发发票或红字发票要节省时间。请注意，为了确保你的发票符合法规要求，在线发票一旦从Tradeshift发出就不可更改（就像纸质发票一样）。"

msgid "[learningemail 4] You know what it''s like when invoicing a customer for the first time !important; **communication is everything**. It''s part of establishing a good relationship. Outline your processes and preferred method of payment upfront. It''ll make things easier for everyone.{0}We recommend including **a short description of your terms** in the \"Note\" field of every Invoice. This can result in faster payments.{0}When switching from old-fashioned paper invoicing to Tradeshift, we recommend **giving your customers an advanced notice** so they''ll be prepared.{0}."
msgstr "第一次向客户发送发票非常重要！**沟通是第一重要的**，这是建立良好合作关系的必要环节。提前列出您的流程以及偏好的付款方式，会减少所有人的工作量。{0}我们建议在发票的备注栏中列入**条款简述**，以获得更快的付款。{0}当你从老式的纸质发票过渡到Tradeshift，建议**提前给你的客户发一个通知**，让他们有所准备。{0}。"

It is however best practice to provide as much data as is available including the suppliers tax/legal identifier, address, key contact information, Invoice Volume, Internal Supplier ID / Vendor Code.<br/>Your supplier master data should be in a structured data file (XLS,CSV, Pipe or Tab Delimited), with one line per company and the size of the file should not exceed 5MB."
